  "body": "According to [deposit receipt spec](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/develop/specs/deposits.md#deposit-receipt),\r\n> With Regolith, this depositNonce field must always be included.\r\n\r\nRegolith started at [block 6825766](https://goerli-optimism.etherscan.io/block/6825766). [Ref](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/op-geth/blob/7d8421c82481eebf4eb3153b57a97e9713ddd5d6/params/config.go#L41)\r\n\r\nHowever, deposit transactions(type = `0x7e`)'s receipts do not contain `depositNonce` field after regolith.\r\n\r\nTested at RPC: https://goerli.optimism.io and also alchemy's endpoint.\r\n\r\nExample RPC request:\r\n```bash\r\ncurl --location 'https://goerli.optimism.io' \\\r\n--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\r\n--data '{\r\n\t\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\r\n\t\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\r\n\t\"params\":[\r\n\"0x4dde3647b5cfb1dc55d1ec27a486bcc080dbc7ab3961c58d5bc1b7302199b34d\"\r\n\t],\r\n\t\"id\":1\r\n}'\r\n```\r\n\r\nResponse:\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"result\": {\r\n    \"blockHash\": \"0x1c865534ac82a3c449b2e1406d8640dcb489e00e8318e1bec4c609d4dbf2866c\",\r\n    \"blockNumber\": \"0x6fb23d\",\r\n    \"contractAddress\": null,\r\n    \"cumulativeGasUsed\": \"0xb735\",\r\n    \"effectiveGasPrice\": \"0x32\",\r\n    \"from\": \"0xdeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddead0001\",\r\n    \"gasUsed\": \"0xb735\",\r\n    \"logs\": [],\r\n    \"logsBloom\": \"\",\r\n    \"status\": \"0x1\",\r\n    \"to\": \"0x4200000000000000000000000000000000000015\",\r\n    \"transactionHash\": \"0x4dde3647b5cfb1dc55d1ec27a486bcc080dbc7ab3961c58d5bc1b7302199b34d\",\r\n    \"transactionIndex\": \"0x0\",\r\n    \"type\": \"0x7e\"\r\n  },\r\n  \"id\": 1\r\n}\r\n```\r\nIt should be\r\n```json\r\n{\r\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n    \"id\": 1,\r\n    \"result\": {\r\n        \"blockHash\": \"0x1c865534ac82a3c449b2e1406d8640dcb489e00e8318e1bec4c609d4dbf2866c\",\r\n        \"blockNumber\": \"0x6fb23d\",\r\n        \"contractAddress\": null,\r\n        \"cumulativeGasUsed\": \"0xb735\",\r\n        \"depositNonce\": \"0x31ba14\",   <- mandatory field\r\n        \"effectiveGasPrice\": \"0x32\",\r\n        \"from\": \"0xdeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddeaddead0001\",\r\n        \"gasUsed\": \"0xb735\",\r\n        \"logs\": [],\r\n        \"logsBloom\": \"\",\r\n        \"status\": \"0x1\",\r\n        \"to\": \"0x4200000000000000000000000000000000000015\",\r\n        \"transactionHash\": \"0x4dde3647b5cfb1dc55d1ec27a486bcc080dbc7ab3961c58d5bc1b7302199b34d\",\r\n        \"transactionIndex\": \"0x0\",\r\n        \"type\": \"0x7e\"\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n```",
